scene.message:
Nanjo: I'll grant Kasai's{nl}
character isn't the best.{waitkey}{clearbox}She made a show of flaunting{nl}
that she was dating Naito,{nl}
after all.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Naito's got the looks{nl}
AND he's a good guy. Galls{nl}
me, but he's a real nice guy!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: True, I was surprised{nl}
when Naito and Kasai started{waitkey}dating. Kasai never showed{nl}
any sign of it.{waitkey}{clearbox}If anything, the one who{nl}
liked Naito was so...{wait_fr:48}{nl}
Hey, what about the hospital?{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Hey, isn't it about{nl}
time you gave up on Naito?{waitkey}{clearbox}He ran off with her, for{nl}
sure! It's been two months!{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Naito was popular{nl}
with the girls,{waitkey}{clearbox}but two months back he just{nl}
stopped coming to school.{waitkey}{ret}

Student: That's a lie! Naito's{nl}
being tricked by Kasai!{waitkey}Because deep down that girl's{nl}
got a really nasty side!{waitkey}{ret}

Student: Kasai was Sonomura's{nl}
best friend, right?{waitkey}{clearbox}If you're visiting her, ask{nl}
about all that, would you!{waitkey}{ret}
